Description: A computational toolkit to import, process, integrate, and analyze
    climatic, air quality, and health data from the Brazilian Unified Health
    System (SUS). Climasus4r automates the most laborious steps of data analysis,
    ensuring standardized and reproducible research, specifically aligned with
    the strategic goals of the INCT Conexão - Amazônia project.
